# Hallmark (Room TBA)

UI edits on matched files: read [.cursor/skills/hallmark/SKILL.md](../skills/hallmark/SKILL.md) and [.cursor/skills/hallmark/references/room-tba.md](../skills/hallmark/references/room-tba.md).

## Quick gates (product UI)

- No `transition: all` — list properties explicitly.
- No hover `transform: scale()` on **toolbar / flyout / chip** controls (pins on map canvas exempt per room-tba.md).
- No decorative gradients on buttons; skeleton loaders and brand splash gradients are OK.
- Typography: body stays readable (≥4.5:1); do not swap Inter for another default sans without reason.
- Verify **320px** after layout changes; see [map-layout.mdc](map-layout.mdc).

## Verbs

- User says **audit** → score target, punch list only, no edits unless they ask.
- User says **redesign** → in-place visual layer; preserve routes, stores, copy intent.
- Polish pass after fixes → Impeccable `/impeccable polish` optional; do not duplicate feedback surfaces.

Ponytail still wins on diff size; Hallmark wins on slop tells.
